snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Scalebreaker First Look
snippet.description: We’re excited to give you a sneak peek of Scalebreaker, ESO’s upcoming DLC game pack. Scalebreaker features two new dungeons – Moongrave Fane and Lair of Maarselok – and leading the tour will be Dungeon Lead Mike Finnigan and Senior Writer Randy Begel. Moongrave Fane takes you through the ancient ruins of a forgotten Khajitti faith, and Lair of Maarselok sends you into the jungles of Tenmar. If you want to be one of the first to see a preview of these upcoming dungeons, don’t miss this show!
